{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the demo version of Crestfall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo contains all online and offline game modes from the full game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your account and any online progress will be carried over to the full game automatically. Any offline progress will not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>You have 60 seconds to set up your side of the board, then, the game begins</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459290/extras/Setup.gif?t=1737569986\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Advance your way up the board, capturing territory</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459290/extras/Movement.gif?t=1737569986\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Deploy your forces across a compact battlefield</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459290/extras/Deploy.gif?t=1737569986\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Attack and discover your opponent's pieces</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459290/extras/Attack.gif?t=1737569986\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Unleash powerful supports to turn the tide of battle mid-game</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459290/extras/Support.gif?t=1737569986\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From air-striking your opponent's General to airlifting your Flag out of danger. Each piece has unique ranks and abilities letting you craft devious strategies to outmaneuver your opponent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_p